Package: mini-commander
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Simplified clone of Midnight Commander
 Mini Commander is a very simplified clone of Midnight Commander
 for Linux. It provides a dual-pane file manager interface with
 basic file operations in a terminal environment.
 .
 This is a lightweight alternative to the full Midnight Commander,
 suitable for embedded systems and minimal installations.
